# Assembled per-harness bundles (regenerated by scripts/sync-source.js, also
# at publish time via prepack). Every release wipes and regenerates — they're
# not source of truth, so the whole src/ tree stays out of git. The committed
# manifest catalog lives at <repoRoot>/manifests/<harness>/v<version>.json
# (repo-level, decoupled from installer/). sync-source.js restores those into
# installer/src/<harness>/manifests/ at the start of every run so the npm
# tarball still ships every prior version via files: ["src/"].
src/

.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
desktop.ini

